Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Excellent access via the now open 41st Avenue Interchange and Nisku Spine Road. Close proximity to the Edmonton International Airport. Heavy duty 8” reinforced floors. Food grade processing/sanitation rooms with aluminum wall paneling. Dedicated packaging areas with clean room wall. (PVC) panels. Portion of warehouse area air conditioned. Crane ready up to 25 ton per bay. Up to 16,000 sq. ft. of office space available.

Manufacturing plant for sublease. Great location in Nisku Industrial Park, with easy access to Highway 625, Airport Road, and the QEII Highway. The building features substantial electrical service, up to 2,000 amp, 277/480 volt. High quality improvements throughout the building. Large volume of complementary office furniture and warehouse racking. Numerous bridge and jib cranes throughout the plant.
